17:03
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1012000' id='t-1012000'>Now I want to say,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1014000' id='t-1014000'>this is not easy.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1017000' id='t-1017000'>It's hard to hold onto this feeling,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1019000' id='t-1019000'>really hard.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1021000' id='t-1021000'>I guess in some way,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1023000' id='t-1023000'>I sort of believe it's supposed to be hard.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1025000' id='t-1025000'>Doubt and fear always creep in.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1028000' id='t-1028000'>We think someone else, someone smarter than us,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1031000' id='t-1031000'>someone more capable,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1033000' id='t-1033000'>someone with more resources will solve that problem.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1036000' id='t-1036000'>But there isn't anyone else;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1038000' id='t-1038000'>there's just you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1041000' id='t-1041000'>And if we're lucky,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1043000' id='t-1043000'>in that moment,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1045000' id='t-1045000'>someone steps into that doubt and fear,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1048000' id='t-1048000'>takes a hand and says,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1051000' id='t-1051000'>&quot;Let me help you believe.&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
