<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1054000' id='t-1054000'>Jason Harley did that for me.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1057000' id='t-1057000'>Jason started at DARPA</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1060000' id='t-1060000'>on March 18th, 2010.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1062000' id='t-1062000'>He was with our transportation team.</span>
