<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1313000' id='t-1313000'>It took them 10 full prototypes</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1315000' id='t-1315000'>to get something that would actually fly.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1317000' id='t-1317000'>But there's something really interesting</span>
